app.py file :
We can run the app.py by right clicking on it.
Before that we need to install flask to run the code. Flask is used to run the web applications using python.
We can install it by using the command  Pip install flask in command prompt( cmd).
After flask has been imported and assigned to app, then if we run the app.py code we are calling localhost which means we will get the link for criminal identification 
home page web application.
whenever this command is executed it goes to index() function and it return index.html file.
template file :
In footer html some description will be added.
In header.html buttons are present.
In index.html, home page has been created using python and flask.
further login, register boxes will be created for Authorities and Users and database will be created to store user, authority and criminal details.


